Rsps have to move on, give the other frameworks a try and make runescape private servers better. This also include some minigames such as, pest control. Fight pits. Duel arena. Clan wars. Barrows. What did i actually do?
Server side
I rewritted a lot of the formulas, checked over the minigames fixed some major bugs in fight caves. The following was cracked out when sanity released and i putted my own back there. The combat system was great i also powered up dharok & verac abit so they are like the other styles, the mage minigame is also added to the teleport list. added clan wars, and some of the duel arena options was broke they are now fixed. I also moved home from Edgeville to 3 other places so there isnt only 1home, you can chose between "Varrock, Falador, Lumbridge", the start of Castle wars is added. MORE TO COME IN V3
Client side
I made godwars maps load, the real mapdata also. Anchor now work togheter with a lot of more clothes & items from the 474 itemList. I looked in the client and i found something wich caused some lagg while you was switching from ranged to melee its now fixed.
